---
// packages/web/src/components/chains/WhyItMatters.astro
//
// Explains why Drivechains matter for Bitcoin's future.
// Three key benefits: security, scalability, capabilities.
---

<section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-20">

  <h2 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold md:text-4xl">
    Why It <span class="text-ecash-400">Matters</span>
  </h2>
  <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-xl text-center text-gray-400">
    Drivechains expand what Bitcoin can do without changing
    Bitcoin's core protocol.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-16 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">

    <!-- Bitcoin-Level Security -->
    <div class="flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900/40 p-8">
      <div class="flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-ecash-800/40 bg-ecash-950/30">
        <svg class="h-7 w-7 text-ecash-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="mt-5 text-lg font-semibold text-white">
        Bitcoin-Level Security
      </h3>
      <p class="mt-3 flex-1 text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        Every sidechain is secured by Bitcoin's full SHA-256d hashrate
        through merged mining. No new consensus mechanisms, no additional
        trust assumptions. The same miners that secure Bitcoin secure
        every Drivechain.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Modular Scalability -->
    <div class="flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900/40 p-8">
      <div class="flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-ecash-800/40 bg-ecash-950/30">
        <svg class="h-7 w-7 text-ecash-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 3.75v4.5m0-4.5h4.5m-4.5 0L9 9m10.5-6v4.5m0-4.5h-4.5m4.5 0L15 9m-10.5 6v4.5m0-4.5h4.5m-4.5 0L9 15m10.5 0l-5.25 5.25M19.5 15v4.5m0-4.5h-4.5" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="mt-5 text-lg font-semibold text-white">
        Modular Scalability
      </h3>
      <p class="mt-3 flex-1 text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        Instead of overloading a single blockchain, Drivechains distribute
        functionality across purpose-built chains. Each chain can optimize
        for its specific use case — payments, privacy, smart contracts —
        without bloating the mainchain.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- New Financial Capabilities -->
    <div class="flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900/40 p-8">
      <div class="flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-ecash-800/40 bg-ecash-950/30">
        <svg class="h-7 w-7 text-ecash-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="mt-5 text-lg font-semibold text-white">
        New Financial Capabilities
      </h3>
      <p class="mt-3 flex-1 text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        Bitcoin DeFi, Bitcoin privacy, Bitcoin smart contracts,
        Bitcoin prediction markets — all secured by Bitcoin miners,
        all accessible through a single wallet. Drivechains make
        Bitcoin a complete financial platform.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
